.TH "libnvme_host_set_pdc_enabled" 9 "libnvme_host_set_pdc_enabled" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvme_host_set_pdc_enabled \- Set Persistent Discovery Controller flag
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" libnvme_host_set_pdc_enabled
.BI "(libnvme_host_t h "  ","
.BI "bool enabled "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "h" 12
Host for which the falg should be set
.IP "enabled" 12
The bool to set the enabled flag
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
When \fBlibnvme_host_set_pdc_enabled\fP is not used to set the PDC flag,
\fBlibnvme_host_is_pdc_enabled\fP will return the default value which was
passed into the function and not the undefined flag value.
